04:22.963 --> 04:27.332
But it's still a place
that we have to go,

04:27.334 --> 04:29.001
everyday,

04:29.003 --> 04:31.169
and it can feel like...

04:31.838 --> 04:33.739
you're stuck.

04:33.741 --> 04:35.440
Like you're not allowed
to be yourself

04:35.442 --> 04:37.776
all of the time, right?

04:39.712 --> 04:41.947
What are some other places
that can feel like that?

04:41.949 --> 04:44.149
- Sorry, Miss Stevens?
- Yes, Margot.

