04:58.765 --> 05:00.799
What did you think
of the ending?

05:01.467 --> 05:02.601
Nice try, man.

05:02.603 --> 05:04.102
- Calm down, I read it.
- Guys...

05:04.104 --> 05:06.305
Just like you read
<i>The Great Gatsby?</i>

05:06.307 --> 05:07.406
Guys!

05:07.408 --> 05:08.907
Why don't you just
watch the movie?

05:08.909 --> 05:11.510
Actually, watching movies aren't
really a safe way to cheat.

05:11.512 --> 05:12.778
Just 'cause someone doesn't talk

05:12.780 --> 05:14.313
every time they
feel like talking,

05:14.315 --> 05:15.847
doesn't mean they
didn't read the book.

05:15.849 --> 05:17.049
Guys!

05:18.651 --> 05:20.319
Done?

05:20.321 --> 05:21.887
Let's get back to the book.

05:22.555 --> 05:24.256
What did you think?

05:24.957 --> 05:26.425
Of the ending?

05:26.427 --> 05:27.893
Mm-hmm.

05:28.828 --> 05:30.162
I love it.

05:32.932 --> 05:34.299
This is what I wanna do.

05:34.301 --> 05:35.500
So I checked with
the front office,

05:35.502 --> 05:37.536
and they have the petty
cash all ready to go,

05:37.538 --> 05:38.603
and they double checked

05:38.605 --> 05:40.005
and all our permission
slips are in.

05:40.007 --> 05:41.807
So we're all set for
the drama competition.

05:41.809 --> 05:42.941
Thank you.

05:42.943 --> 05:43.942
You're welcome.

05:43.944 --> 05:45.610
And we're leaving after
third period, yes?

05:45.612 --> 05:46.845
That's the plan.

05:46.847 --> 05:48.380
And thank you for taking us.

05:48.382 --> 05:50.615
I had to ask three
other teachers

05:50.617 --> 05:52.517
before you volunteered to come.

05:53.186 --> 05:54.286
Billy?

06:04.263 --> 06:06.531
- Hi, Margot.
- Hi, Billy.

06:08.000 --> 06:10.602
Billy, when are we doing
the <i>Gats</i> make up?

06:11.237 --> 06:12.304
Shit!

06:12.306 --> 06:13.538
Margot?

06:13.540 --> 06:16.541
- Oh, right. See you both at...
- 12:00?

06:19.112 --> 06:20.379
First of all, no cursing.

06:20.381 --> 06:21.980
Second of all, did
you finish the book?

06:21.982 --> 06:22.982
Yes, I did.

06:24.283 --> 06:25.684
It's been two weeks.

06:25.686 --> 06:27.486
I don't wanna fail you.
What's going on?

06:27.488 --> 06:28.754
